## Summary

Sentinel Manifold is made available so individuals, community builders,
students, researchers, nonprofits, and small businesses can inspect it, test it,
learn from it, modify it, and use it for their own work.

Large-scale commercial use is not granted by this community license. If you want
to embed Sentinel Manifold in a commercial product, hosted service, search
engine, model gateway, AI platform, customer-facing SaaS product, or other
revenue-generating tool outside the grants below, you need a separate commercial
license from the copyright holder.

This summary is explanatory. The operative grants are below.

